Often the wood will have minor imperfections and other natural characteristics of real wood. There could be slight cracks where the slats come together. Any of the text on our signs can be customized. All of our images have the look and feel of real vintage signs. They can hang outside as long as they are in a sheltered area.

Original vintage image designed to look like an antique sign. The image is printed directly to a distressed wood panel made from 1/2 inch tongue and groove slats. Often the wood will have minor imperfections and other natural characteristics of real wood. There could be slight cracks where the slats come together. Any of the text on our signs can be customized. All of our images have the look and feel of real vintage signs. They can hang outside as long as they are in a sheltered area.
Vintage sign printed directly to a distressed wood panel. This image can be customized by adding or changing any of the text.

Rustic vintage football sign printed directly to a distressed wood panel that has knots and other imperfections. We end up printing right over these imperfections which gives each sign the look and feel of a real vintage sign. No two are the same! Often people ask us "Are these originals?" All of our signs can be customized making each vintage sign personal and original. Each designed in the style and look of a historical period using different font styles, colors, and vintage layouts.
